{
  "stem": "16571.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 315.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I seem to be immune to it now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things are getting really in a state.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My son got married two and a half years ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've got a photo of 12 of us on this particular photo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Four of them passed away in the last two and a half years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you get immune to things, you-- you-- in the camps as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You get used to the idea to get beatings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You get used to being shotted upon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You get used to being number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't a matter of having to get, you just got used to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's how it went all through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were lucky, because we were only in about 13 and 1/2 months, whereas a lot of my friends, as I said before, were in it a long time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from going back to where I left off, my brother suddenly start writing to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wrote back, and said, you know, from here, came over on child transport and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was about-- I-- I learned years later that he went to White Alps in the snows to Palestine, and he got in in 1947.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Israel the very first time in '55, which was 11 and 1/2 years since I saw them last.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I saw them, we were all grown up with our own children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whereas, 11 years, 11 and 1/2 years, when you are 40 or 50 means nothing, There I was, going on a boat from south of France on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It took about five days to arrive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was salty showers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I love the sun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was sitting in the-- in the shower and sunbathing, in the shower and sunbathing.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
